    <div class="swiper-wrapper stop-swiping">
      <div class="swiper-slide">
        <div class="faq_item">
          <div class="faq_text">
            · Is Lyra compatible with Alexa or Google Assistant?
          </div>
          <div class="faq_sub_text">
            Yes, this smart Lyra floor lamp is compatible with the Govee Home app, Alexa,  and Google assistants(not included). You can voice control the floor lamp.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq_item">
          <div class="faq_text">
            · Does this floor lamp come with a remote controller?
          </div>
          <div class="faq_sub_text">
            Yes, this Lyra floor lamp comes with a remote.<br>
            Here are the 5 basic functions with the remote,<br>
            1)On/Off;2)Brightness;3)Color variation;4)Music mode;5)Cool/ Warm white
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq_item">
          <div class="faq_text">
            · Can I control it remotely?
          </div>
          <div class="faq_sub_text">
            Yes, this smart floor lamp supports WiFi connection. Even when you are not at home, just keep this device connected to your home wifi, you can still control it remotely.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq_item">
          <div class="faq_text">
            · Can this sync up with the light strips?
          </div>
          <div class="faq_sub_text">
            Yes, our Govee Home app supports Smarts (group control) with 3 functions: 1)On and Off; 2) Color mode; 3)Brightness.
