            The Lyra floor lamp comes with a US plug adapter and does not support USB port.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="swiper-slide">
        <div class="faq_item">
          <div class="faq_text">
            · Can this show multicolors simultaneously?
          </div>
          <div class="faq_sub_text">
            Yes, this is an RGBICWW floor lamp that supports multicolors in a line with gradient transition. Plus, you can choose one of 25 Scene Mode or DIY Mode through the Govee Home app.
