            This lamp can instantly transform your room with a 2200K-6500K color temperature for reading, relaxing, and more.
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq_item">
          <div class="faq_text">
            · Does this floor lamp support music mode?
          </div>
          <div class="faq_sub_text">
            Yes, the Lyra floor lamp supports 6 different music effects, you can choose the one you desire. 
