        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="swiper-slide">
        <div class="faq_item">
          <div class="faq_text">
            · How to install this floor lamp, do you have a quick installation guide?
          </div>
          <div class="faq_sub_text">
            Yes, besides the quick guide attached in the product package, we also have an installation guide video for your reference, please take a look. 
